<HEADLINE> DPR. Korea's Han Breaks World Obstacle Running Record </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ZAGREB, Croatia, August 10 (Xinhua) -- Han Hye Gyong of DPR.
Korea on Tuesday broke the world record for the women's obstacle
running in the military pentathlon competition at the Military
World Games here.
</P>
<P>
Han clocked two minutes 20.6 seconds to shave 0.3 seconds off
the previous mark set by China's Shen Liping at the World Military
Pentathlon Championships in Beijing last year.
</P>
