followed by Han in the second place at 2,163.8 and another DPR
Korean athlete Myong Gum Sun at third in 2,159.6.
</P>
<P>
DPR Korea led the team standings with 3,364.7 points, over 100
points ahead of China, who collected 3,222.6 after two events.
