<HEADLINE> More Foreign Tourists Come to Romania to View Solar Eclipse </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUCHAREST, August 11 (Xinhua) -- Total solar eclipse attracted
20-25 percent more foreign tourists to Romania than a year ago,
the official Rompres news agency reported Wednesday.
</P>
