"a fresh blow" to the Indo-Pakistan relations.
</P>
<P>
"We have taken a positive step forward and we wanted to
establish some kind of atmosphere of trust and resumption of
dialogue, but all this has suffered a fresh blow to our efforts,"
he told reporters here.
</P>
<P>
Charging that the Indians have a record of aggressions, he said
they are being true to their record with the latest incident.
</P>
<P>
