<HEADLINE> Kuala Lumpur Stocks Close Mixed </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KUALA LUMPUR, August 11 (Xinhua) -- Share prices on the Kuala
Lumpur Stock Exchange closed mixed Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
At the close, the 100-quality stocks Composite Index added 4.85
points to 688.50, the all-share Emas index rose 0.44 of a point to
175.14 points, the Industrial Index added 1.75 points to 1,187.10
and the Second Board Index lost 0.56 of a point to 147.63.
</P>
<P>
Losers led gainers by 387 to 275 while 130 counters were
unchanged and 127 counters untraded.
</P>
<P>
The day's total turnover stood at 333.666 million shares valued
at 840.341 million ringgit (about 221.142 million U.S. dollars)
against Tuesday's 371.101 million shares valued at 803.361 million
ringgit (about 211.41 million dollars). 
</P>
