<TEXT>
<P>
The two sides of the Taiwan Straits are closely related
economically, Wu says, but Lee's remark only serves his ugly
political ambitions and neglects the interests of Taiwan investors
and it will be condemned by compatriots on both sides of the
Straits.
</P>
