Compatriots, says that Lee Teng-hui has increased tensions across
the Straits with his "two states" remark and pushed to separate
Taiwan from China. It hurts exchanges and cooperation across the
Straits and goes against the wishes of the people of Taiwan for
stability, peace, and development.  
