<HEADLINE> Foreign Exchange Rates in Pakistan </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, August 11 (Xinhua) -- The following are major
foreign exchange rates against the Pakistani rupee released
Wednesday by the Treasury Management Division of the National Bank
of Pakistan.
</P>
<P>
U.S. dollar  51.9000/51.4000
