events for 22-man crews over 400 meters, 12-man crews over 800
meters and 12-woman crews over 800 meters. Indonesia now has won
four of the six races staged so far, and Myanmar has won two. In
the closest race, Indonesia's 22-man crew beat Myanmar by 2.44
seconds in one minute, 22.12 seconds.
