Yellow River to bring benefits to future generations.
</P>
<P>
During an inspection tour of northwest China's Shaanxi Province
on August 5-8, Zhu urged local governments to take concrete
measures, including the return of farmland and the cordoning off
of hills for afforestation and grass planting, to improve the
local ecological environment.
</P>
