exposes the illegality of the Falun Gong cult and its activities,
stressing that the socialist rule of law shall not be infringed
upon.
</P>
<P>
 Xinhua Daily Telegraph
</P>
<P>
-- Officials and the general public across China continue to
lash out at Li Hongzhi and his Falun Gong organization, with an
increasing number of people coming to realize the true nature of
the cult.
</P>
<P>
Falun Gong has fooled and instigated practitioners to besiege
and disturb government departments and the media in the past few
years.
</P>
<P>
The April 25 gathering at Beijing severely disturbed the
routine work of the Party and government institutions, and
jeopardized the city's stability, in violation of the Constitution
and other regulations, said Tian Shuyu, a judge at the Higher
People's Court of north China's Hebei Province.
</P>
<P>
