of his 6-3, 6-4 win over Russian teenager Marat Safin. Chang is
unseeded as he looked to turn around a season in which he has won
half of his 28 matches.
</P>
<P>
Coming off a quarterfinal showing in Montreal, American Jim
Courier beat slumping Croatian Goran Ivanisevic 7-6 (7-1), 6-2.
</P>
<P>
